", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75280177_1012617213990979_1732549949916101256_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FpiZTk26Z3QQ7kNvgHEDnDE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBYmbdkfHdYd_7z0o1DcmhobdQ_SpXKsTZBatLXj5WeLQ&oe=67824638"}, {"file_name": "image5.png", "id": "27882995044633476", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974864_27882995047966809_2560160188894003364_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WyjcEvq-h8YQ7kNvgGZsNIX&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBfs8SI1RBEzFhxv9C4ErxP9mw4kEVtXqxPcfpC4WjdAg&oe=67824479"}, {"file_name": "image2.png", "id": "410575135384874", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974821_410575138718207_8230945586108737660_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KAWgtSMxaSAQ7kNvgExBtSK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDrdaLpYMW40zfNhvJoMcbukx47yg4EklfwcFnsdlOIqQ&oe=67826258"}, {"file_name": "image1.png", "id": "1057387732496751", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75540501_1057387735830084_2190979014283040881_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vEEM2nb_ynsQ7kNvgG9URvl&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD7Hs8MCad-mwzLqslL1Y21Jb1pE_FoieFHHQ0S7YmcNA&oe=67826D73"}, {"file_name": "image4.png", "id": "1151089155995496", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974848_1151089159328829_2039739925044486928_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZXhBdPYjAo8Q7kNvgHWegez&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDIUFpg1SIMUc4sJ8laUxcrOIsD-VLZchC7LJZWwRr9uA&oe=67823F2F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Keyart_2560x1440.png", "id": "1984373528679847", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974591_1984373532013180_122028893976097645_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3UvgukNBPXUQ7kNvgFeVsUC&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYACW9pi3x0QS76CnGd2lLRhHpoMps8XHuMeaVtbQQPCzA&oe=6782523B"}, "display_name": "My Monsters Demo", "keywords": ["Monsters", "Third", "Free", "Puzzle", "My"], "long_description": "My Monsters is an action-adventure VR game featuring *100% hand-painted art*, creating a visually stunning world full of fantasy and surrealism.\n\nAt the heart of the game lies a deep narrative exploring humanity's greatest inner struggles\u2014anxiety, fear, and loneliness. As the player, you are transported to Onirium, a *dream-like realm* where you encounter Moti, a frightened little monster with no memory.\n\nIn My Monsters, you\u2019re never alone. *Team up with your inner monster*, Moti, to face a variety of enemies, solve intricate puzzles, and overcome challenges in a shared journey. This partnership mechanic fosters a powerful connection with Moti, requiring empathy and courage to navigate obstacles and reveal fragments of a *meaningful dreamlike tale*. Every stage introduces new aspects of this bond, allowing players to experience moments of self-discovery and emotional depth.\n\nKey Features in the Demo:\n\n\n\u2694\ufe0f  Combat Enemies: Engage in dynamic combat with enemies.\n\n\ud83e\udde9  Solve Puzzles: Challenge your critical thinking and problem-solving skills.\n\n\ud83c\udf19  A Dream-like Tale: Uncover a touching, emotional narrative that delves into themes of self-reflection and growth. \n\n\ud83c\udfa8  100% Hand-Painted Art: Every visual element in the game is carefully crafted by hand, creating a beautiful, one-of-a-kind experience. \n\n\ud83e\udd1d  Team Up with Your Inner Monster: Build a meaningful relationship with Moti, using teamwork, empathy, and courage to overcome every challenge.\n\n*THE GAME IS IN DEVELOPMENT, AND ITS CONTENT MAY CHANGE.*", "short_description": "My Monsters is a VR action-adventure game featuring stunning 100% hand-painted art. In this demo, you\u2019ll explore Onirium, a dream-like world filled with emotional depth, as you face humanity's greatest inner monsters like anxiety and fear. Meet Moti, a scared little monster with no memory, and team up to battle enemies, solve puzzles, and overcome challenges. Unravel fragments of a dreamlike narrative as you journey together. The game is currently in development, and its content may change."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mymonsters.ludact.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ludact", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://mymonsters.ludact.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "528142316460358"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8686086238127538"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036697_535483152192630_2729698551779994031_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=g49c9mdOrVwQ7kNvgFTMb6J&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB7cQpBcglMzIwmChnWlW1gbWGdZPtC-oI37lBi2nwf7Q&oe=67826283"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "My Monsters Demo", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "GAMES", "id": "2743326035925534"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Adventure", "id": "2691890164460465"}, {"topic_name": "Action", "id": "45978